        m_Untranslated: A Different Gizmo Style
      Text:
        m_Untranslated: "Unfortunately there is no DrawCircle gizmo, and while a
          sphere is good enough, Unity does provide different mechanics for drawing
          circles (it\u2019s often the case with Unity that there are a variety of
          completely different approaches to similar tasks \u2013 which can be pretty
          frustrating at times)."
